graph TD
    A[Manager triggers Approval Process] --> B{Is Outstanding Balance > 0?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Trigger Validation Rule blocks approval]
    C --> D[Add error: Cannot approve application with outstanding balance]
    B -- No --> E[Approve application]
    E --> F[Status set to Approved]
    F --> G[Trigger: ApplicationService.updateStudentStatusOnApproval]
    G --> H[Update linked Student.Status to Active]
    F --> I[Trigger: ApplicationTriggerHandler.sendApprovalEmails]
    I --> J[Dispatch notification email via NotificationService]
